### behelit
* port-forwarding with mullvad
* link between godhand and apostle
* hosted on a raspberry pi
* always active

### godhand
* gui application to connect to a behelit
* can issue commands to an active apostle

### apostle
* does not maintain a constant connection to a behelit
  but checks in every 30 seconds or so and checks for new orders
* has a ID
* discrete